</p>
<p>As part of the GIAN programme (<a href=3D"http://www.gian.iitkgp.ac.in/"=
>http://www.gian.iitkgp.ac.in/</a>), a 1 week course on Vehicle Dynamics an=
d Control would be conducted at IIT Madras, the details of which are:</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Title: Vehicle Dynamics and Control.</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Course Faculty: Prof. Rajesh Rajamani, University of Minnesota, USA (<a =
href=3D"http://www.me.umn.edu/~rajamani/">http://www.me.umn.edu/~rajamani/<=
/a>).</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Dates: May 30, 2016 to June 3, 2016.<br>
</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Link to Course Brochure: <a href=3D"http://www.gian.iitkgp.ac.in//files/=
brochures/BR1451624242GIAN_Brochure_Vehicle_Dynamics_and_Control_Shankarram=
_ED_30May_to_3June_2016.pdf">
http://www.gian.iitkgp.ac.in//files/brochures/BR1451624242GIAN_Brochure_Veh=
icle_Dynamics_and_Control_Shankarram_ED_30May_to_3June_2016.pdf</a></p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Last Date for Registration through the GIAN website: March 31, 2016.</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Intimation of Selected Participants: April 28, 2016.</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Students of IIT Madras selected to attend this course can&nbsp;credit it=
